title: Revival of Russia’s Military Might 'Sensation of the Year' in the West
text: Bursts of Russian bombs in the Middle East have seemingly stricken ordinary Americans “explosive waves,” becoming a kind of psychological bomb in the West. There hasn’t been such a reaction towards Russia since the launch of Sputnik 1 and Yuri Gagarin flight to space, Russian columnist Vladimir Soloviev wrote. ...
